title: DR. MARTENS X TEENAGE MUTANT NINJA TURTLES: DONATELLO
description:
Dr. Martens have teamed up with Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles to create a 4-piece capsule collection inspired by the four characters.

The Donnie boot, inspired by Donatello. He stands for skating, sleeping and eating.
